snippet.title: The Devourer: Hunted Souls | Game Trailer
snippet.description:
The Devourer: Hunted Souls Official Game Trailer in nice and smooth 60 FPS!

Do you like indie horror games? We are two developers from Germany and we are excited to announce our upcoming multiplayer horror game where you play as one of five paranormal investigators. Can you and your friends lift the curse and free the forest?

Powered by Unreal Engine 5.

Early Acces launch date: Between Q2 and Q3 2023.

Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2309400/The_Devourer_Hunted_Souls
Join our Discord: https://discord.gg/5Jp46KY9sd
Support us on Kickstarter: https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/ztekstudio/the-devourer-hunted-souls
